OL,5,G```FFONTYS TILBURG TOURNAMENTG```````` 
OL,7,GGoing into the first restday, World    
OL,8,Gchampion Garry Kasparov continues to   
OL,9,Gset the pace in the tournament, and he 
OL,10,Gholds a slender half-point lead        
OL,11,Gfollowing a draw with Alexander        
OL,12,GOnischuk in round four.                
OL,14,FNearest rival Vladimir Kramnik, fell   
OL,15,Fbehind in the fourth, as he was held to
OL,16,Fa draw with top British player GM      
OL,17,FMickey Adams.                          
